{
  "texts": [
    "Automatic generationThe PGN model [36] is selected to be the generation model for the KGCPN.",
    "In general PGN models, the parameters of the word embedding matrix are randomly initialized, which may lead to poor performance and elevated training costs.",
    "In addition, the issue of polysemy is also urgently needed to be addressed.",
    "To tackle these challenges, we incorporate the BERT model for parameter initialization.",
    "The multi-head attention mechanism is employed to obtain contextual semantic information, making it more dynamic and enabling more effective feature extraction."
  ]
}